Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.90,0:00:30.97,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 你究竟要睡到什麼時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.67,0:00:33.88,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我剛剛才睡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.77,0:00:35.97,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,剛剛才睡？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.42,0:00:38.72,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你忙什麼忙到現在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.49,0:00:41.79,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我製做了天空
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.01,0:00:43.94,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,天空？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.20,0:00:56.49,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.18,0:00:58.12,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,很厲害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.73,0:01:00.13,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,該說厲害…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.01,0:01:06.50,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼又睡了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.61,0:01:08.23,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,再讓我睡一會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.29,0:01:09.05,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.05,0:01:09.94,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我馬上就起來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.94,0:01:11.86,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 快起床…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.90,0:02:57.36,FBT,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,480)\pos(960,720)}通向黎明的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.45,0:03:35.62,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.99,0:03:37.34,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這是誰害的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.26,0:03:42.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我去買個午飯後連人影都不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.93,0:03:50.00,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得買了麵包再回去教室太麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.00,0:03:55.36,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得屋頂才是更遠…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.28,0:04:16.27,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,很漂亮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.19,0:04:20.43,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,沒差 從哪裹看不都是一樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.80,0:04:25.45,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我還在想她拿著便當到哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.88,0:04:27.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,紗繪你太大聲了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.32,0:04:31.12,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那兩個人在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.51,0:04:35.30,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那我們又在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.58,0:04:40.00,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 公園附近有艘很大的船吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.45,0:04:44.30,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那個港口每次都有別樣的氣氛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.53,0:04:46.96,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是個拍照的好地方哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.51,0:04:48.50,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,先不說這個 馬上就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.50,0:04:49.06,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.26,0:04:50.97,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那個地方也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.22,0:04:52.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那條河邊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.77,0:04:57.13,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,登上大橋旁的臺階 就能把整個城市一覽無遺了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.61,0:05:00.90,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,天晴的時候那兒的景色真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.11,0:05:01.14,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 喂 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.33,0:05:01.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.57,0:05:03.28,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.74,0:05:07.15,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,今天探望姐姐時 你能先去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.45,0:05:08.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.60,0:05:12.08,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,送修的照相機修理好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.32,0:05:14.15,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,所以得去店裡取回
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.66,0:05:16.66,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這種事不是什麼時候去都行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.96,0:05:21.25,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊 邂逅是不知道會在何時何地出現的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.71,0:05:23.57,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你是指和天空的邂逅？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.01,0:05:24.95,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,還會有其他的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.20,0:05:27.06,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.34,0:05:31.35,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉真名 辦完事後我一定會去的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.55,0:05:34.93,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 又這麼說 上次不是也沒來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.63,0:05:37.12,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,今天一定會來的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.81,0:05:38.90,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.73,0:05:41.55,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.03,0:05:51.88,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 一點也沒改
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.54,0:05:59.74,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.29,0:06:02.50,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,難道真名被甩了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.84,0:06:05.02,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.04,0:06:42.99,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,天空什麼的 我最～討厭了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.01,0:06:45.96,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,喔？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.04,0:06:57.57,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你們在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.10,0:06:59.87,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,沒…嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.04,0:07:08.34,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,被他逃掉了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.94,0:07:13.87,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,森宮君被真名告白後一定覺得很不好意思啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.16,0:07:16.88,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,所以午休以後就翹課了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.88,0:07:20.58,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,行了 行了 雖然不知道你又在妄想什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.80,0:07:25.25,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,但最近你們在一起的時間變多了是個不爭的事實啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.87,0:07:27.71,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,連塔子也是 你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.59,0:07:30.37,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我們都是去同一家醫院
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.47,0:07:32.18,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,經常在一起也是無可厚非嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.70,0:07:36.14,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我得去醫院 先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.93,0:07:38.06,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,怪人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.14,0:07:42.08,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,再試一次比較好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.48,0:07:44.99,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,森宮君很喜歡天空
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.31,0:07:50.24,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,比起草莓樣式的 星星和雲樣式的效果會更好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.24,0:07:54.69,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,又來了 又說這些莫名其妙的話了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.12,0:07:56.08,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.33,0:07:59.49,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,她沒弄明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.65,0:08:01.15,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真是遲鈍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.91,0:08:07.13,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,紗繪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.05,0:08:10.65,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,把你的給我看！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.51,0:08:15.30,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 讓我看！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.00,0:08:22.98,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 都怪紗繪要遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.65,0:08:34.74,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.92,0:08:37.34,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,果然在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.99,0:08:40.47,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真名 安靜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.79,0:08:50.01,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 我這就帶小依回病房去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.47,0:08:51.38,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.13,0:08:55.95,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.85,0:09:02.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…我想他一會就來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.52,0:09:04.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真名小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.10,0:09:08.47,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.07,0:09:14.50,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,小依這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.09,0:09:48.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.99,0:09:58.49,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,我想吃魚子醬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.44,0:09:57.57,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這也是個難題啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.42,0:10:10.33,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好 看來沒問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.72,0:10:24.54,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是真名啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.56,0:10:29.90,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真名 抱歉 我馬上就去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.35,0:10:32.21,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你果然沒發現啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.57,0:10:33.16,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你指什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.73,0:10:36.57,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,探病時間早就過了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.86,0:10:38.57,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.57,0:10:44.02,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,總之 明天一定要好好和蒼乃道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.78,0:10:47.73,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 真難辦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.96,0:10:49.92,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐生氣了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.73,0:11:46.11,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來 從哪開始找呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.90,0:11:54.64,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,明明把錢放進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.15,0:11:58.88,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,1…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.62,0:12:06.77,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好疼…好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.08,0:12:13.01,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.04,0:12:18.45,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,1…2…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.72,0:12:30.46,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,紅色
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.96,0:12:34.64,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因為你一頭鑽進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.15,0:12:40.48,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,只是有點紅腫已經很慶倖了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.52,0:12:42.70,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不是說那個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.14,0:12:45.18,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我說過想吃魚子醬的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.66,0:12:48.37,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,魚子醬 鮭魚子不都一樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.74,0:12:50.02,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.70,0:12:52.17,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼你不吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.58,0:12:54.68,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,吃倒是吃的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.80,0:13:01.64,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我果然還是想吃鵝肝醬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.90,0:13:02.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,鵝肝醬？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.30,0:13:04.12,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你去買
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.88,0:13:05.94,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這個不吃了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.13,0:13:09.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我會吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.76,0:13:14.23,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀 公主很不高興嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.85,0:13:15.70,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.32,0:13:18.16,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,只是長途旅行有點累而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.05,0:13:20.56,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去找個地方藏起來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.12,0:13:22.77,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,明天你來找我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.82,0:13:27.27,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不要忘了鵝肝醬哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.83,0:13:32.26,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,連我的那份都拿走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.30,0:13:55.21,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.89,0:14:01.68,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,蛋糕？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.19,0:14:05.32,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 明天是蒼乃的生日吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.02,0:14:09.95,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我想帶個到醫院去 怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.74,0:14:12.40,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣的話姐姐會很高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.12,0:14:16.85,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 那麼接下來我們去商店選購吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.19,0:14:20.47,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來？ 不是明天去？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.75,0:14:24.17,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,當然了 必須得事先預訂才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.71,0:14:29.19,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不一定要預訂的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.43,0:14:32.28,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.42,0:14:33.83,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.72,0:14:39.22,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你不會說今天也有事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.48,0:14:41.49,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,當然我一定會去醫院的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.96,0:14:42.68,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.02,0:14:46.26,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 我要利用之前的時間…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.61,0:14:47.49,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.40,0:14:49.95,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,等…等等 真名小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.08,0:14:55.40,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,最近生日蛋糕的種類很多 我們得多花點時間認真選
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.29,0:14:58.62,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真夠嗆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.33,0:15:00.23,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你指哪個？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.81,0:15:17.35,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,快走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.49,0:15:19.28,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,最新型的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.27,0:15:26.81,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到會買一整塊的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.36,0:15:29.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,生日蛋糕嘛 這不是理所當然的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.24,0:15:33.03,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,或許選個小一點的比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.48,0:15:36.52,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,小的話就只能插幾根蠟燭了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.45,0:15:39.01,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你準備插幾根啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.36,0:15:42.68,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,明天真是令人期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.35,0:15:44.14,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,期待什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.54,0:15:46.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,蒼乃姐的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.13,0:15:47.99,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.72,0:15:49.77,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.13,0:15:55.81,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,小依在自己生日前一天總是緊張得睡不著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.48,0:15:58.42,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,小依是不是有點怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.02,0:16:00.21,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,沒這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.40,0:16:02.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我深信那樣才算正常
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.61,0:16:09.51,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.72,0:16:11.65,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真名
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.39,0:16:15.65,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.93,0:16:19.56,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 你要到什麼時候才能叫對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.12,0:16:21.33,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.61,0:16:24.16,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直適應不了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.79,0:16:25.75,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,行了 行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.01,0:16:27.50,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 身體…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.05,0:16:35.05,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 昨天…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.59,0:16:38.50,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,還有 雖然有點那個 今天特地
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.81,0:16:41.14,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,給 是雙胞胎人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.59,0:16:42.56,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,很可愛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.34,0:16:47.97,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,二人眨眼的地方很吸引人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.27,0:16:49.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.59,0:16:51.42,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,明天…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.68,0:16:52.84,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,當然我會來的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.37,0:16:55.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,明天是姐姐的生日嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.74,0:16:57.51,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我準備了秘密的禮物哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.82,0:16:58.77,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.33,0:17:01.14,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我說過沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.63,0:17:05.66,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人的「沒問題」啦「當然」啦這些話完全沒有說服力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.92,0:17:06.75,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.77,0:17:08.55,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天不就說謊了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.96,0:17:10.30,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,下次絕對不會了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.30,0:17:11.10,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,盡說謊話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.13,0:17:09.42,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,明天真是值得期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.00,0:17:12.18,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,一點點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.76,0:17:17.73,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,蒼乃也說說嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.05,0:17:19.81,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這和姐姐沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.97,0:17:23.40,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,上次也是 明明是上課卻不在教室裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.56,0:17:25.65,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然在屋頂上拍照片
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.21,0:17:27.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.98,0:17:28.77,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.44,0:17:32.23,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,看來小依不是站在我這邊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.50,0:17:36.18,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼小依要站在你那邊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.80,0:17:37.54,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.41,0:17:39.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是依人不好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.04,0:17:40.59,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.91,0:17:41.94,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.62,0:17:46.43,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我不討厭依人拍的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.33,0:17:48.21,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.16,0:17:53.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 下次我把照片也帶來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.63,0:17:55.57,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,如果那樣的話 最好是黎明的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.38,0:17:57.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,黎明？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.74,0:17:58.19,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.55,0:18:00.32,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.76,0:18:03.76,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,為了姐姐我會鼓足幹勁帶一張很美的照片來的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.27,0:18:07.22,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的人偶看來姐姐也很喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.59,0:18:08.76,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼說來…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.11,0:18:10.00,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,看來是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.32,0:18:12.59,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.54,0:18:32.54,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好不容易找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.82,0:18:55.25,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,總覺得不對勁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.74,0:18:57.54,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,看看其他的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.13,0:19:22.17,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.85,0:19:27.73,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,今天就到此為止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.58,0:19:35.46,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.01,0:19:41.65,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,本以為還有不少的呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.81,0:19:52.59,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,果然還是去拍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.50,0:19:57.03,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,請給我這個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.22,0:20:05.54,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,名字是四方茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.18,0:20:07.72,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,住所是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.35,0:20:10.37,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？住所？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.50,0:20:15.22,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 住所就寫教會
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.74,0:20:27.12,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好～吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.49,0:20:30.81,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 味道好像有點不夠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.62,0:20:35.91,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 之後去哪裡好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.77,0:21:37.77,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,能趕上嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.88,0:21:59.06,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,他在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.59,0:22:09.54,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.60,0:22:19.52,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,差勁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.45,0:22:33.01,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,才這麼早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.17,0:22:44.42,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真名
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.04,0:23:19.91,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,1…2…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.65,0:23:23.14,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.29,0:23:27.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你在幹什麼？
