Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.76,0:22:24.72,IMJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}でも　時は同じ思いだけを
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.47,0:22:36.14,IMJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}あ　描きつづければ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.82,0:22:52.38,IMJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}誰も知らず
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.99,0:23:03.52,IMJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}日が射すまでに
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.06,0:23:19.79,IMJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}そっと　そっと
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.53,0:23:30.53,IMJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}こころが感じてた
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.29,0:20:49.11,IMCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}淺波輕搖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.46,0:21:00.34,IMCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}蕩漾起我的心潮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.56,0:21:16.21,IMCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}靜靜地　靜靜地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.00,0:21:27.45,IMCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}就算消失也不再困擾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.62,0:21:43.25,IMCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}但那殘存的感情　該如何是好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.27,0:21:54.28,IMCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}啊　那色彩會褪去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.76,0:22:24.72,IMCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}然而　有時會把同一種心情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.47,0:22:36.14,IMCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}啊　久久描繪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.82,0:22:52.38,IMCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}誰也不曾知曉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.99,0:23:03.52,IMCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}直到陽光照耀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.06,0:23:19.79,IMCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}靜靜地　靜靜地
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.53,0:23:30.53,IMCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}心裡有了一絲預感
